features: Versatile Home Choice: In the living room, this end table serves as a small coffee table for guests. In the bedroom, it functions as a practical nightstand for bedtime reading materials etc

Safe Power Strip: The power strip is embedded in the shelf below the top, featuring 1 outlet, 1 USB port and 1 Type C port. This thoughtful design ensures that multiple electronic devices can be charged simultaneously and securely

Space-Saving Storage Solution: The compact nightstands allows for full utilization of small corners or gaps between sofas. The 3-tier open design enables organized categorization of items, creating a tidy and pleasant living space

Reliable Stability: YATINEY selects high-class chipboard and sturdy metal frame to cast this end table with good stability and durability. With 4 bottom adjustable feet, this side table can stand stable on various ground without leaving scratches

Quick Installation: The nightstands has a simple structure and comes with a detailed assembly manual, clearly numbered parts and necessary assembly tools. It lets you enjoy the fun of DIY and have a practical side table in no time

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Six weeks after purchase
reviews.reviewText: I purchased two of these as end tables. I was skeptical regarding the quality. I have been surprised with the finish endurance of daily use. The tables ship in smaller boxes and are a cinch to assemble. Instructions are fairly easy to follow, and all of the hardware matched well with the pre drilled holes. Everything tightened together snugly. The sturdiness is pretty solid. These end tables are used for table lamps and light book storage mainly. I would discourage placing beverages directly on the table top. Coasters are definitely encouraged. Power strip and charging station work as advertised. I am satisfied with the value and overall performance of my purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect For Me
reviews.reviewText: This turned out to be perfect for a small space and my gaming gear.It was super easy to put together. It comes with an Allen wrench but you will need a small Phillips screwdriver as well.Instructions were perfect. They even remind you which way to hold it based on the holes when assembling it. It's pretty easy to strip the threads so be careful to not over tighten.I used a cable clamp and zip ties to run the power cord off to the side as well.
